snippet.title: OTHER: Her Loving Embrace - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Support us on KICKSTARTER: https://bit.ly/2mHMV40

OTHER: Her Loving Embrace is a role-playing game with a twist - while the battles are turn-based, you directly control your characters in a platforming arena.

Any abilities you discover along the way can be used both in and out of battle! Take down enemies in creative and complex ways as you explore your way across a daunting world, brimming with intrigue and danger.

Download the DEMO: https://bit.ly/2nJutb9
Steam: https://bit.ly/2nFdZkl
Website: http://www.otherrpg.com/
Twitter: http://twitter.com/otherRPG
